data.description: Step into your dream home and fall in love with this unique open floorplan!  Boasting almost 2800sqft of living space PLUS a sub basement, this is one beautiful home.  Meticulously updated and maintained with new interior paint throughout, new carpet, stainless appliances, fresh exterior paint, HVAC, ROOF, HWH and gutters all just two years old. The spacious main living area offers tons of natural light, vaulted ceilings and an elegant fireplace. Picture yourself entertaining in this fabulous kitchen with room for everyone around the table or in the sitting area. The center island makes the perfect spot to set up a buffet or just enjoy extra counter space while chatting with family and friends. Don't miss the generously sized master bedroom complete with large windows that look out into the woods behind. The master bath is a spa like retreat with a jetted tub, dual sinks and XL walk-in closet. Two generous secondary bedrooms and a full bath share that level as well. Step downstairs to the family room! You will love retreating here for movie night with the backdrop of a cozy fireplace. Another full bath and 4th bedroom share this level as well. Walkout to the patio or up to the deck and enjoy the tranquility of nature behind your home. Sprinkler system keeps it all lush and green. On your way out don't miss the neighborhood pool! Wells Fargo 3.75% FHA assumable loan may be available! This is a lovely place to call home!
